step_deterministic_bool.solution:
Theorem step_deterministic :
  deterministic step.
Proof.
  unfold deterministic. intros x y1 y2 H1 H2.
  generalize dependent y2.
  induction H1; intros y2 H2; inversion H2; subst;
    try reflexivity;
    try (inversion H1);
    try (inversion H3);
    try (f_equal; apply IHH1; assumption).
Qed.

combined_step_deterministic.solution:
Theorem combined_step_deterministic: (deterministic step) \/ ~ (deterministic step).
Proof.
  left. unfold deterministic.
  intros x y1 y2 H1 H2.
  generalize dependent y2.
  induction H1; intros y2 H2; inversion H2; subst;
    try reflexivity;
    try (inversion H1);
    try (inversion H);
    try (exfalso; inversion H0; subst; inversion H1);
    try (f_equal; apply IHH1; assumption).
  - inversion H3.
  - inversion H4.
  - inversion H; subst; inversion H5.
Qed.
